<item>
            <title>[PIG-1395] Mapside cogroup runs out of memory</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-1395</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In a particular scenario when there aren&apos;t lot of tuples with a same key in a relation (i.e. there aren&apos;t many repeating keys) map tasks doing cogroup fails with GC overhead exception.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
